multiLocaleTitle.en_US: Senior Recruitment Consultant - Hays Banking and Financial Services

included.description: Rebecca is responsible for banking recruitment, including middle office(products design/risk/compliance) and back office (global market/cash and trade/custodian/transaction/operation);PE and VC firms, investment banking M&A positions.\n\nRebecca has strong relationship with clients that result in highly successful recruitment partnerships.\n\nHays – the world’s leading recruiting experts in qualified, professional and skilled work.\n\nWe operate across the private and public sectors, dealing in permanent positions, contract roles and temporary assignments. We are market leaders in Asia Pacific and the UK and one of the market leaders in Continental Europe and Latin America.  As of the 31st January 2014, we employed 7800 staff operating from 240 offices in 33 countries across 21 specialisms.  Our deep expertise across a wide spectrum of specialized industries and professions makes us unparalleled recruiters in the world of work.

included.description: The Talent Company is a global member firm of Career Partners International – a leading consultancy with more than 300 locations around the in the world.\n\nWe are an organization comprised of leading Recruitment, Talent Development, Total Rewards and Career Transition experts with proven track records of consulting and organizational success. Our collective resources, vast experience and extensive industry knowledge enhance our ability to deliver outstanding value to our clients.\n\nWe provide our clients with full range of Human Resources solutions including:\n\nFIND - Search, Talent Pipelining, Interim and Recruitment Advisory\n\nKEEP - Executive Coaching and Leadership Development\n\nREWARD - Compensation, Benefits and Total Rewards\n\nTRANSITION - Career Transition Programs and Planning\n\nFor more information about The Talent Company, please visit www.thetalent.co or email me at rebecca.liu@thetalent.co \n\nRecruitment Lead specializing in: \n*Mid to Senior Professionals within Total Rewards, Financial services industry.\n*Senior operation roles including General Manager, Plant Manager and Supply Chain Operations Senior Leadership Role. \n*Talent Acquisition Strategy & Delivery\n*Talent Management
